description:
&lt;p&gt;To provide clerical and typing support as requested. Operation of telephone systems - where applicable. This would involve receiving and relaying telephone and other messages for staff and liaising with other agencies if requested. To communicate in a sensitive empathetic manner when dealing with members of the public, patients and clients. To sort and distribute mail and ensure provision of a photocopying service for staff as requested/required. To ensure that filing systems are kept up-to-date.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ability to speak Welsh is desirable for this post; Welsh and/or English speakers are equally welcome to apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date: 12th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
